data.description: Get your checklist out! Large ACCESSIBLE lot, Circle Driveway, private cul-de sac, Low taxes, NO HOA, and PAID off Solar. I think this might be the one you want to see. What stands out about this home, is the fact you can access the nearly one-acre lot from multiple sides. If you are looking to build an ADU separately from the main house this lot is perfect! If you are looking for light farming / agricultural this lot is perfect for that as well! Coming in just under an acre, this parcel seems much larger because of its allocation. The main house is a nice blend of old and new, with upgraded features like a new master bathroom and upgraded floors, while still maintaining a traditional farm house look.
